Interface MeterReadingRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<MeterReading,String>, MeterReadingRepositoryCustom, org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.MongoRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<MeterReading,String>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<MeterReading>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<MeterReading,String>
@Repository public interface MeterReadingRepository extends org.springframework.data.mongodb.repository.MongoRepository<MeterReading,String>, MeterReadingRepositoryCustom
Repository interface for MeterReading entities.

Extends MongoRepository to provide CRUD operations and includes custom query methods for retrieving meter readings based on specific criteria.

Also extends MeterReadingRepositoryCustom to include custom repository methods that are not derived from method naming conventions.

Custom query methods:

  • findTopByProviderIdOrderByTimestampDesc(String providerId): Retrieves the latest meter reading for a given provider.
  • findByProviderIdAndTimestampBetween(String providerId, String startTime, String endTime): Retrieves all meter readings for a given provider within a specified time range.
